{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rev|4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","chapter":4,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":1,"text":"After this I looked, and there in heaven was an open door. The first voice that I had heard speaking to me like a trumpet said, “Come up here, and I will show you what must take place after this.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":2,"text":"Immediately I was in the Spirit, and there was a throne in heaven and someone was seated on it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":3,"text":"The one seated there had the appearance of jasper and carnelian stone. A rainbow that had the appearance of an emerald surrounded the throne.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":4,"text":"Around the throne were twenty-four thrones, and on the thrones sat twenty-four elders dressed in white clothes, with golden crowns on their heads.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":5,"text":"Flashes of lightning and rumblings and peals of thunder came from the throne. Seven fiery torches were burning before the throne, which are the seven spirits of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":6,"text":"Something like a sea of glass, similar to crystal, was also before the throne.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":7,"text":"The first living creature was like a lion; the second living creature was like an ox; the third living creature had a face like a man; and the fourth living creature was like a flying eagle.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":8,"text":"Each of the four living creatures had six wings; they were covered with eyes around and inside. Day and night they never stop, saying,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":9,"text":"Whenever the living creatures give glory, honor, and thanks to the one seated on the throne, the one who lives forever and ever,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":10,"text":"the twenty-four elders fall down before the one seated on the throne and worship the one who lives forever and ever. They cast their crowns before the throne and say,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":4,"verse":11,"text":"Our Lord and God,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","chapter":4,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,4,5,7,9,11],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Throne Room of Heaven"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:4:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After this I looked, and there in heaven was an open door. The first voice that I had heard speaking to me like a trumpet "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 19:19","book":"Exo","chap